<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Foodie Haven</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
    <header class="bg-white shadow">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 tracking-wider">Foodie Haven</h1>
            <nav class="mt-4 text-center">
                <a href="/" class="text-white hover:text-blue-500 mx-4 w-20 h-15 bg-red-500 rounded-lg inline-block">Home</a>
                <a href="/product" class="text-white hover:text-blue-500 mx-4 w-20 h-15 bg-red-500 rounded-lg inline-block">Menu</a>
                <a href="/product" class="text-white hover:text-blue-500 mx-4 w-20 h-15 bg-red-500 rounded-lg inline-block">Order</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="text-white hover:text-blue-500 mx-4 w-20 h-15 bg-red-500 rounded-lg inline-block">Contact</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">About Us</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
                Welcome to Foodie Haven, your ultimate destination for delicious and convenient online food delivery. Our mission is to bring you the best culinary experiences right to your doorstep, offering a diverse range of dishes that cater to all tastes and preferences.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Story</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
                Foodie Haven was founded in 2020 by a group of food enthusiasts who wanted to make high-quality, diverse cuisine accessible to everyone. We started as a small kitchen with big dreams, and today, we are proud to serve thousands of satisfied customers every day.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What We Offer</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
                Our menu is a curated collection of the best dishes from around the world, prepared with fresh ingredients and utmost care. Whether you're craving a hearty Italian pasta, a spicy Indian curry, or a classic American burger, we have something to satisfy your taste buds.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Why Choose Us?</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                <li>Fast and reliable delivery</li>
                <li>Fresh and high-quality ingredients</li>
                <li>Wide variety of dishes to choose from</li>
                <li>Easy and convenient online ordering</li>
                <li>Exceptional customer service</li>
            </ul>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Commitment</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
                At Foodie Haven, we are committed to providing you with an exceptional dining experience, whether you're ordering lunch at the office or dinner for a family gathering. We strive to exceed your expectations with every order, and we value your feedback to continually improve our service.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact Us</h3>
            <p>
                Have questions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us at <a class="text-blue-500 hover:underline" >info@foodiehaven.com</a> or call us at (123) 456-7890.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-6 mt-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Foodie Haven. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
